00:00:00,530 --> 00:00:04,120
Welcome to the class where you get serious about web development.

2
00:00:04,120 --> 00:00:07,180
By the end of this course, your code will be professional, and

3
00:00:07,180 --> 00:00:09,340
professional code is what will get you your next job.

4
00:00:09,340 --> 00:00:14,160
You'll be able to build an organized application, both with or

5
